Every application for an import licence lodged in accordance with  Regulation (EC) No 1977/95 for the period from 1 July 1995 to 30 June 1996 shall be granted to the  following extent, expressed as bone-in beef:
(a)  0,504  % of the quantity requested for beef imports intended for the manufacture of  'preserves` as defined by Article 1 (2) (a) of Regulation (EC) No 1977/95;
(b)  49,213  % of the quantity requested for beef imports intended for the manufacture of products  as defined by Article 1 (2) (b) of Regulation (EC) No 1977/95.
